.TH netstat 1
.SH NAME
\*Lnetstat\*O \- Displays network statistics.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
.sS
\*Lnetstat\*O
\*O[\*L-Aan\*O]
\*O[\*L-f\*O
\*Vaddress_family\*O]
\*O[\*L-p\*O
\*Vprotocol\*O]
.\" Begin Digital-specific information
.\" Commenting out system and core arguments per QAR 10743.
.\" \*O[\*Vsystem\*O]
.\" \*O[\*Vcore\*O]
.\" End Digital-specific information
\*O[\*Vinterval\*O]
.PP
\*Lnetstat\*O
.\" Begin Digital-specific information CORRECTION
\*O[\*L-adHmMnrstu\*O]
.\" End Digital-specific information CORRECTION
\*O[\*L-f\*O
\*Vaddress_family\*O]
\*O[\*L-p\*O
\*Vprotocol\*O]
.\" Begin Digital-specific information
.\" Commenting out system and core arguments per QAR 10743.
.\" \*O[\*Vsystem\*O]
.\" \*O[\*Vcore\*O]
.\" End Digital-specific information
\*O[\*Vinterval\*O]
.PP
\*Lnetstat\*O
\*O[\*L-ntd\*O]
\*O[\*L-I\*O
\*Vinterface\*O]
.\" Begin Digital-specific information
